
<p><big style="font-size: 130%; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-variant:small-caps">’T was</span></big> later when the summer went<br>
Than when the cricket came,<br>
And yet we knew that gentle clock<br>
Meant nought but going home.<br><br>
’T was sooner when the cricket went<br>
Than when the winter came,<br>
Yet that pathetic pendulum<br>
Keeps esoteric time.</p>
